## üîß Configuration

Create `config.yaml`:

```yaml
search:
  default_sources:
    - pubmed
    - arxiv
  max_results: 100

embeddings:
  model: all-MiniLM-L6-v2
  device: auto

evidence:
  use_llm: false
  ensemble_strategy: weighted_average

offline:
  enabled: true
  sync_on_connect: true
```

